{"tid":1256292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Magic Leap 將中國前員工告上法院，指控剽竊技術回國開公司","createTime":"2019-06-25T02:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:46:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea2372ba7982e4653ec6fd9571c4410336f18e7e","tid":1256292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"Magic Leap 將中國前員工告上法院，指控剽竊技術回國開公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/06/24/magic-leap-sues-chinese-ex-empolyee-for-steal-ar-glasses-design/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F06%2F24%2Fmagic-leap-sues-chinese-ex-empolyee-for-steal-ar-glasses-design%2F&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=be8f30a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/06/24/magic-leap-sues-chinese-ex-empolyee-for-steal-ar-glasses-design/</a><br />\n<br />\n開發擴增實境（AR）頭戴式裝置的美國新創公司 Magic Leap 控告前員工剽竊技術，並回到中國創辦自己的 AR 裝置公司。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nMagic Leap 不只是一般的新創公司，這家開發 AR 和 MR 裝置的公司已獲得超過 20 億美元投資。Magic Leap 在美國加州北部地方法院提出告訴，控訴 2016 年離職的員工徐馳（Chi Xu）利用公司機密資料，迅速開發了輕巧且符合人體工程學設計的混合現實（MR）眼鏡，且產品與 Magic Leap 的設計非常相似。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《富比士》（Forbes）雜誌報導，徐馳創辦總部位於北京的杭州太若科技有限公司（Nreal），並在 2019 年的消費電子展（CES）展出產品，號稱比 Magic Leap 的產品更輕。這款產品 Nreal Light 預計在 2019 年底開始上市，且售價僅 499 美元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Magic Leap 研發長達 7 年時間，終於在 2018 年 8 月推出第一款產品 Magic Leap One。Magic Leap 宣稱徐馳在公司工作約 13 個月，不僅沒有負起工作責任，還陰謀策劃獲取專業資訊以回到中國創辦自己的公司。「雖然 Nreal 宣稱在兩年內開發產品 Nreal Light，但 Magic Leap 投入多年時間、數億美元的研發經費和數百名的工程師才開發出這項技術。」控告文件寫道。</span><br />\n<br />\n徐馳被控告違反契約、詐騙和不公平競爭，公司 Nreal 也列為被告，Nreal 和徐馳都沒有立刻對這起訴訟提出回應。如今又一起美國公司指控中國公司竊取智慧財產權的案例，再度反映中美間的緊張局勢並非空穴來風，技術剽竊可說是雙方僵持不下的重要原因。"},{"pid":"c6ed47d9365017548e71d51673f7e1fd6e09ae75","tid":1256292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:57:42.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7f1c60c89a91d818ef351be708ca9993296cfc","tid":1256292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賺完啦"},{"pid":"194059a3a54a8f46adf863a1709c4e8f15c2ce5f","tid":1256292,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:13:11.000Z","msg":"鬼佬真係on9喎，偷左咁多年全世界都知仲請支那人"},{"pid":"cfd980528f10f6bc24177fb9fe98d25392805531","tid":1256292,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔告返你咪偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dddb7649bc84758fc60cd4dc0ca9f9c2c5713b","tid":1256292,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"194059a3a54a8f46adf863a1709c4e8f15c2ce5f","tid":1256292,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:13:11.000Z","msg":"鬼佬真係on9喎，偷左咁多年全世界都知仲請支那人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:20:54.000Z","msg":"中國人：外國人只是見不得中國強大"},{"pid":"95263052f1509fbbe2b75cbacc4ae5505568cdee","tid":1256292,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}